{"tid":2189772,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"胞弟為警員 私家偵探涉連環非禮女童","createTime":"2020-09-05T06:23:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-05T18:10:34.000Z","uid":240362,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"22ed29662ab8424a549f300280e6083aa24750a7","tid":2189772,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:23:48.000Z","msg":"年輕男私家偵探涉嫌藉詞拍攝校服校章，摸女童胸部及掀裙底非禮，女童受驚通知家人報警。警方事後拘捕涉案疑犯，揭發至少有四名事主，最年輕者不足10歲；並找到多段校服女生被摸短片。私家偵探被控非禮等五罪，今在九龍城裁判法院提堂，案件押後至本月10日，待警方進一步調查，包括安排認人手續，其間被告須還柙警方看管。據悉被告胞弟任職警員。<br />\n<br />\n被告申請保釋，但遭裁判官梁少玲拒絕，案件將於本月10日轉往西九龍裁判法院再訊。據了解，被告有兩名胞弟，其中一人是警員。控方申請將被告還柙警方看管，以進行認人手續；辯方則希望可還柙懲教署，容許被告女友探訪。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/VOK2ZGOK4JA5RLA4SANRRYLLVM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FVOK2ZGOK4JA5RLA4SANRRYLLVM%2F&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs4yHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=733eb0b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200905%2FVOK2ZGOK4JA5RLA4SANRRYLLVM%2F&h=71c92fe3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200905/VOK2ZGOK4JA5RLA4SANRRYLLVM/</a>"},{"pid":"e5cfc5574ac042a79ff1b0c3e73f1bc8e3a12061","tid":2189772,"uid":201359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:26:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a947b39d4c724359f8c77536fdd071a231268542","tid":2189772,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T06:27:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif